Visualizations of LA County Alumni

Geographic Visualization


This bar graph describes the numbers that are present in the heatmap below. For example, from the bar graph we can see that there are 59 people in Santa Clarita and there is a smaller less colored circle there in the top left corner. Following that logic, we can use this heatmap to pinpoint locations in LA County that have differing levels of alumni.

Boxplots

These graphs are describing the distribution of the alumni age ranges.



Splitting the alumni by gender shows us that there is a very minute age difference between men and women.
